cdata.name: FujiCoin
cdata.desc:
Launched on June 28,FujiCoin is a fully decentralized global payment network. It is a blockchain-based platform, where the users are able to make P2Ptransactions withFJC tokenson a global scale, in 60 seconds.

TheFJCtoken is a Pow (Proof of Work) cryptocurrency that uses the Scrypt-N-Fixed algorithm. It is the token supported by the platform for the users' transactions and will be spendable on the marketplaceunder development by FujiCoin.
